{"tid":545340,"cid":21,"subCid":3,"title":"[Far East Union Vol.3 in HK] MONOEYESxSupper Momentx滅火器xTHE SOLUTIONS","createTime":"2018-01-30T12:11:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T01:53:11.000Z","uid":104721,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ead1b2d53e535b3423e5910a5ffc958efa53c6d3","tid":545340,"uid":104721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T12:11:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/26993838_10155294936904109_2811400328841363869_n.jpg?oh=abb63aa93d12515cc85d3f2c48deb983&amp;oe=5AEBCE24\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F26993838_10155294936904109_2811400328841363869_n.jpg%3Foh%3Dabb63aa93d12515cc85d3f2c48deb983%26oe%3D5AEBCE24&h=21c0557b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>港日台韓聯手策劃　 Far East Union Vol.3 首度來港</strong><br />\n已舉辦了兩年的跨國巡迴計劃Far East Union，今年香港將首度加入這個強大陣容。四個地方的樂隊包括日本的MONOEYES、韓國的THE SOLUTIONS、台灣的滅火器和香港的Supper Moment，將會在今年三月巡迴起跑。最後一站來到香港的Music Zone作巡迴的尾場，樂迷門萬勿錯過！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>MONOEYES </strong><br />\n日本知名搖滾歌手細美武士 (ELLEGARDEN、the HIATUS) 2015年組成的新團MONOEYES首度來港。由細美武士(vocal, guitar）、一瀬正和（ASPARAGUS、the HIATUS / drum）、Scott Murphy（Scott &amp; Rivers / bass, chorus）、戸高賢史（ART-SCHOOL / guitar）四人組成的MONOEYES，每位成員都是實力卓越的猛人。2017年夏天推出了第二張專輯《Dim The Lights》，並展開了全國廿多場巡迴公演。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>THE SOLUTIONS</strong><br />\n韓國獨立音樂大廠Happy Robot Records旗下的搖滾組合THE SOLUTIONS 由Park Sol (vocal)、Naru (guitar/chorus)、Park HanSol (drums.)、Kwon OhKyung (bass)四人所組成。在2012年發行首張同名專輯後曾得到Mint Paper Awards 2012的Rookie of The Year獎項，備受注目。以全英文創作的The SOLUTIONS不受任何曲風束縛，將90s的brit-pop、美式alternative rock、2010的J-POP混和調合，轉化成為自己的獨有「Future Pop」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>滅火器 Fire Ex.</strong><br />\n來自台灣高雄的滅火器對於香港聽眾來說不會陌生。這支成立了十多年的搖滾樂團，包括主唱大正、吉他手鄭宇辰、貝斯手陳敬元和鼓手吳迪，曾奪得台灣金音獎「最佳演出現場獎」、KKBOX「年度風雲獨立精神獎」，以及金曲獎「最佳年度歌曲」等。2015年成立自己的廠牌，2016二度登上Summer Sonic的舞台。2017年辦了首屆火球祭音樂節，與Supper Moment結緣。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Supper Moment</strong><br />\n香港樂隊 Supper Moment 2017年在香港各大頒獎禮拿到豐富成績後，2018年的目標除了繼續將音樂帶到更多不同地方發生外，更會在這個春天發表新的專輯。這次首度和日韓台三地的勁旅巡迴同台演出，必定毫無保留，敬請期待！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>票價 (全場企位)</ins><br />\n$450<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://venue.cityline.com/utsvInternet/internet/action/event.do?actionFwd=eventDetail&amp;event=23871&amp;actionType=5&amp;lang=TW&amp;fuiSwfzk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvenue.cityline.com%2FutsvInternet%2Finternet%2Faction%2Fevent.do%3FactionFwd%3DeventDetail%26event%3D23871%26actionType%3D5%26lang%3DTW%26fuiSwfzk&d=XUrsYqOM6maeyggfL9i%2BrcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=5cf73bf7\" target=\"_blank\">http://venue.cityline.com/utsvInternet/internet/action/event.do?actionFwd=eventDetail&amp;event=23871&amp;actionType=5&amp;lang=TW&amp;fuiSwfzk</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">召喚細美fans</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"563a08ad6ad4b1516864f2c39e35e35339a139d3","tid":545340,"uid":104721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T00:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e5ae072af3f82e65a7bad10c4de65b68798002b","tid":545340,"uid":104721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T10:17:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dac77a0d51c3ce4bd3db1a3bfe5688e53760e1c","tid":545340,"uid":68925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T10:35:28.000Z","msg":"飛已買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e24ebbef17bdea280fa909e88dc22a2c5506f8","tid":545340,"uid":104721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T03:44:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/ass